{"type":null,"faqId":33923,"title":"如何自定义智灵？","answer":"<p>您也可以为\"智灵\"选定其他工作模式。请进入\"设置-&gt;智灵\"中设置。\n<br>\n例如\"单击\"可以设置为：\n<br>\n打开情景智能\n<br>\n启动智能语音\n<br>\n熄屏快拍（手机黑屏时，单击一次可快速拍照一张。亮屏解锁状态下无法拍照。）\n<br>\n启动录音（短按1次启动录音，再短按一次停止录音。）\n<br>\n启动手电筒（短按1次打开手电筒，再短按一次关闭手电筒。）\n<br>\n截屏（亮屏下短按一次可截屏一张。黑屏下不响应截屏功能。）\n<br>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8625","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748763000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":59,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"智灵,自定义","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}